description: Meet the Donegal man trying to become the first finswimmer to circumnavigate a country.
title: The man swimming around the coast of Ireland
title_page: The man swimming around the coast of Ireland - BBC News
maintext: "We also realise that some of the biggest challenges lie ahead with the worsening weather of the winter and the realisation that the last leg will be completed in the turbulent seas of the Atlantic Ocean, along the Wild Atlantic Way."
